{"word":"Sincerity","slug":"sincerity","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sincerity</b> Does not exempt from guilt<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20'>Gen 20</a><br/><a href='S:Ignorance, Sins of'>Ignorance, Sins of</a> <br/> Forgiveness of enemies must be sincere<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=35'>Mat 18:35</a><br/> Servants must render honest service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=7'>Eph 6:7</a><br/> Whatsoever is done must be in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=31'>1Co 10:31</a><br/> Jesus was an example of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=22'>1Pe 2:22</a><br/> Ministers should be examples of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=7'>Tit 2:7</a><br/> Opposed to fleshly wisdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Co 1:12</a><br/> Should characterize:<br/> - Our love to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=8'>2Co 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=24'>2Co 8:24</a> <br/> - Our love to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=24'>Eph 6:24</a> <br/> - Our service to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=14'>Jos 24:14</a> <br/> - Our faith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=5'>1Ti 1:5</a> <br/> - Our love to one another<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=12&verse=9'>Rom 12:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=22'>1Pe 1:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=18'>1Jn 3:18</a> <br/> - Our whole conduct<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Co 1:12</a> <br/> - The preaching of the gospel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=2&verse=17'>2Co 2:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=5'>1Th 2:5</a> <br/> A characteristic of the doctrines of the gospel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=2'>1Pe 2:2</a><br/> The gospel sometimes preached without<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=16'>Phi 1:16</a><br/> The wicked devoid of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=5&verse=9'>Psa 5:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=55&verse=21'>Psa 55:21</a><br/> Exhortations to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Co 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=1'>1Pe 2:1</a><br/> Prayer for, on behalf of others<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=10'>Phi 1:10</a><br/> Blessedness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=32&verse=2'>Psa 32:2</a><br/> Exemplified:<br/> - By men of Zebulun<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ch 12:33</a> <br/> - By Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=3'>Isa 38:3</a> <br/> - By Nathanael<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=47'>Joh 1:47</a> <br/> - By Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Co 1:12</a> <br/> - By Timothy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=5'>2Ti 1:5</a> <br/> - By Lois and Eunice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=5'>2Ti 1:5</a> "}]}